snippet.title: Celaria - Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
Due to the updates over the past weeks/months to the visuals an updated version of the previous trailer was released. (Visual enhancements include improved outline rendering, a more advanced shading model of the map geometry and player character,subtle high-quality bloom, updated skybox & improved skybox rendering and more)

Stay tuned. There is more to come in the near future (featurewise). :)

Celaria on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1081650/Celaria/

Music created by (and licensed from) "Raspberry Music": https://audiojungle.net/user/raspberrymusic
